### v137: Hotspot Avoidance (Ship Zone Detection)
- Key discovery: clips ships auto-scramble junctions within 15 tiles every 70 ticks
- Junctions outside ship zones persist once aligned → much more valuable
- Implemented: track when our junctions get scrambled back
- Each scramble adds +8.0 penalty to junction's alignment score (max 24.0 at 3+)
- This should reduce wasted hearts on junctions near ships
- Also increased miner retreat safety margin (dist+10 → dist+20)
- Single seed test: 4.12 (227 alignments, 97 scrambles)
